text.paragraph:
In the following listing, events are categorized by body system. Within each body system, events are presented in descending order of frequency. The following definitions are used: 



  infrequent adverse reactions are those occurring on one or more occasion in 1/100 to 1/1,000 patients; 



  rare adverse reactions are those occurring on one or more occasion in fewer than 1/1,000 patients.
